00:35:41.507 --> 00:35:44.476
GAL número um.

00:35:44.510 --> 00:35:45.944
Nomeado pelos
pais de Rick e Marty,

00:35:45.977 --> 00:35:48.180
George e Ann...

00:35:48.214 --> 00:35:50.316
