Craig. Jack.

00:37:44.563 --> 00:37:46.565
É bom te ver, Craig.

00:37:46.598 --> 00:37:48.367
a chegada
do Craig Tester

00:37:48.400 --> 00:37:50.669
e seu enteado, Jack Begley,

00:37:50.702 --> 00:37:52.070
